channel.title: Problems with no-ip
channel.description: I got my own server up, worked really good with hamachi, but doesnt work with no-ip. I made an user at no-ip, set up a server, ran runserver.bat but no1 and even i didnt get into it using the no-ip name. I also got a Trendnet router. I tryed to make something there using some tutos but still nothing... Can some1 kno what is the problem with it?

item.title: Problems with no-ip
item.dc:creator: @Narbscape Narbscape
item.description:
@Narbscape wrote:

what is it you want?

You want to make a hamachi server with a no-ip address? I’ve done that,

//Hamachi and no-ip\

Go into your account settings and set up a domain using your HAMACHI IP! and you’re done.

Note that poeple without hamachi will not be able to connect!

//No-ip only\

Do you have a router?
